snippet.title: The Scrolling Enigma vampire promo
snippet.description:
The Scrolling Enigma is a unique escape game playable on Playdate.

This video depicts a player struggling in the vampire chapter, which is one of the best experience on the Playdate so far. 😎

Buy it here.
https://play.date/games/the-scrolling-enigma/
